Email Addresses ^\w+([.-]?\w+)*@\w+([.-]?\w+)*(\.\w{2,3})+$

start : ^

\w+   : word as 1 or more

()*   : ( ) as 0 or more. 
[.-]?\w+ :  if . or - , word must follow 1 or more

()+  : ( ) as 1 more more

\.\w{2,3} :   . followed by word in count of 2 to 3

end : $


Image Filenames ^\w+\.(gif|png|jpg|jpeg)$

